text: Arvid Soderblom will start in goal tomorrow vs. Winnipeg. Alec Regula will draw into the lineup for Filip Roos. #Blackhawks
Blackhawks will start Soderblom again tomorrow at Winnipeg.  Regula will sub in for Roos rest of lineup the same.
Arvid Sderblom starts tomorrow. Alec Regula in for Roos. Mrazek is getting closer and the LA/Anaheim trip is a possibility for him.
